{"tid":1988878,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國聯邦通訊委員會正審查3間中國國有電訊公司","createTime":"2020-04-25T13:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T15:12:06.000Z","uid":91914,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2e3b0122472c4f647be7a335b91cea7f1279bc11","tid":1988878,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T13:21:28.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國聯邦通訊委員會正審查3間中國國有電訊公司，有可能以國家安全為理由，吊銷它們美國的營運牌照。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦通訊委員會FCC，向中國電信美洲公司、中國聯通美洲公司、太平洋網絡有限公司，以及其全資子公司信通電話美國發出命令，要求它們證明公司的獨立性，不受中國政府控制。它們有30日時間作回應。<br />\n<br />\nFCC主席帕伊在聲明中指，今次行動反映這些公司容易受中國政府利用、影響和控制的深切憂慮，指在網絡安全問題上美國不能夠冒險，FCC可能會以國家安全風險為理由，關閉它們在美國的業務。<br />\n<br />\n美國司法部和其他聯邦機構於周四呼籲FCC，吊銷中國電訊美洲公司在美國的營運牌照。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=388899\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388899&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKgXckNDuUEQQ0Md4EdtPbyE%3D&h=be53e420\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388899&h=becae89f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=388899</a>"},{"pid":"bc25ef455420ec756d76b820d071ac9dec41422a","tid":1988878,"uid":252069,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T13:40:33.000Z","msg":"(重開)香港社會運動需要轉型<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1988467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1988467</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ixjbr30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fixjbr30.jpg&h=3dd23a07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UuJC633.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUuJC633.jpg&h=bd20a436&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7aab11153d79e01d6c413d852c1b7ebd4580cf2e","tid":1988878,"uid":355285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T13:40:55.000Z","msg":"D 中資電訊股同5G股插水未<img src=\"/assets/faces